dditionally, qBittorrent runs and provides the same features on all major platforms (FreeBSD, Linux, macOS, OS/2, Windows). qBittorrent is based on the Qt toolkit and libtorrent-rasterbar library.gversione5.0.2ldownload_urlxyhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/qbittorrent-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizei128.26 MBdbsumx@da3c92693c2c9ea08fd3c850564536114d57fa9fce507375455e757b4ad90a88jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCjcategoriesxNetwork,FileTransfer,P2P©cpkgvquake3e.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namepQuake3e (engine)fpkg_idx5github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.quake3e.dwfs.AppBundlekdescriptionwQuake 3 Enhanced enginepdescription_longyÈThis is a modern Quake III Arena engine aimed to be fast, secure and compatible with all existing Q3A mods. It is based on last non-SDL source dump of ioquake3 with latest upstream fixes applied.

Key features:

* Optimized OpenGL renderer
* Optimized Vulkan renderer
* Raw mouse input support, enabled automatically instead of DirectInput(\in_mouse 1) if available
* Unlagged mouse events processing, can be reverted by setting \in_lagged 1
* \in_minimize - hotkey for minimize/restore main window (win32-only, direct replacement for Q3Minimizer)
* \video-pipe - to use external ffmpeg binary as an encoder for better quality and smaller output files
* Significantly reworked QVM (Quake Virtual Machine)
* Improved server-side DoS protection, much reduced memory usage
* Raised filesystem limits (up to 20,000 maps can be handled in a single directory)
* Reworked Zone memory allocator, no more out-of-memory errors
* Non-intrusive support for SDL2 backend (video, audio, input), selectable at compile time
* Tons of bug fixes and other improvements
* Vulkan renderer based on Quake-III-Arena-Kenny-Edition with many additions:

* High-quality per-pixel dynamic lighting
* Very fast flares (\r_flares 1)
* Anisotropic filtering (\r_ext_texture_filter_anisotropic)
* Greatly reduced API overhead (call/dispatch ratio)
* Flexible vertex buffer memory management to allow loading huge maps
* Multiple command buffers to reduce processing bottlenecks
* Reversed depth buffer to eliminate z-fighting on big maps
* Merged lightmaps (atlases)
* Multitexturing optimizations
* Static world surfaces cached in VBO (\r_vbo 1)
* Useful debug markers for tools like RenderDoc
* Fixed framebuffer corruption on some Intel iGPUs
* Offscreen rendering, enabled with \r_fbo 1, all following requires it enabled:

* ScreenMap texture rendering - to create realistic environment reflections
* Multisample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_multisample)
* Supersample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_supersample)
* Per-window gamma-correction which is important for screen-capture tools like OBS
* You can minimize game window any time during \video|\video-pipe recording
* High dynamic range render targets (\r_hdr 1) to avoid color banding
* Bloom post-processing effect
* Arbitrary resolution rendering
* Greyscale modeldownload_urlxchttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/quake3e.dwfs.AppBundledsizeg8.36 MBdbsumx@e7a5f8b95ba104774f719eeb60f581e1936d0d5c4bf8d92cb78c67fabada2247jbuild_datex2025-05-29 00:00:00 +0000 UTC´cpkgx*ristretto-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameiRistrettofpkg_idxIgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.ristretto-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundlekdescriptionx!Fast and lightweight image viewerpdescription_longxõRistretto ‚Äî —Ö—É—Ç–∫–∞—è —ñ –ª—ë–≥–∫–∞–≤–∞–∂–Ω–∞—è –ø—Ä–∞–≥—Ä–∞–º–∞ –¥–ª—è –ø—Ä–∞–≥–ª—è–¥—É –≤—ã—è—û –¥–ª—è –ø—Ä–∞—Ü–æ—û–Ω–∞–≥–∞ –∞—Å—è—Ä–æ–¥–¥–∑—è Xfce.gversionf0.13.2ldownload_urlxwhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/ristretto-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.54 MBdbsumx@0dd8378e3c8cbf30c8d999fb1612970f339d7b2e6a427d89abeb1819638d3383jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCjcategoriesoGraphics,Viewerßcpkgx'scrcpy-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefScrcpyfpkg_idxFgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.scrcpy-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundleldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/scrcpy-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh39.42 MBdbsumx@f951375172d02cd75d0c7e7e5dd175580038d635bf0c3e0f0075bc7690b28be9jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCßcpkgx'thunar-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefThunarfpkg_idxFgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.thunar-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundleldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/thunar-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.42 MBdbsumx@e5b2ed220778c23238d33f7994c9b7b673d88f53aeb56afc45f4b0c181f8f55fjbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCßcpkgx0xfce4-multicall-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameoXfce4 Multicallfpkg_idxOgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-multicall-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundleldownload_urlx}https://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v120-20250626113137/xfce4-multic